ostom sadašnjem vremenu.</p>","feedback":"<p>Glagoli u prostom sadašnjem vremenu ne završavaju se na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-ing</span>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kao glagol u verbalno-imenstvenom sistemu</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kao glagol u obliku glagolske imenice u prošlom vremenu.</p>","feedback":"<p>Arhaične glagolsko-imenice strukture se koriste za perfektni vremenski oblik ili kao pridev. Ovo nije korišćeno ovde na taj način.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"cafe.png","characters":[{"character":"Maria","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.1-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":11.76,"finishTimestamp":17.26},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":6.5,"dialogue":{"text":"I love exploring many new technologies and improving my skills. It keeps me excited about our projects.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Maria","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":7,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 10","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations","dashedName":"task-10","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-have-a-c